---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Continuum Reverberation in Bright Quasars Using NASA/ATLAS - Steyn et al. (2026)";

import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Continuum Reverberation in Bright Quasars Using NASA/ATLAS</h1>

    <div class="infobox">
      <h3 class="infobox-title">Steyn et al. (2026)</h3>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Type:</th>
          <td>Paper</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>First described:</th>
          <td>2026 (Steyn et al.)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Key Papers:</th>
          <td>
            <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11789">Steyn+2026 (arXiv:2603.11789)</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Abstract summary:</strong> Analysis of high-cadence NASA/ATLAS light curves for 9,498 bright quasars shows inter-band delays ~3× larger than thin-disk predictions; contamination from variable diffuse emission likely contributes. Longer lags correlate with higher Eddington ratios and several spectral indicators.</p>

    <h2>Key findings</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Delays ~3× larger than thin-disk predictions persist at high luminosity</li>
      <li>Diffuse emission contamination likely widespread</li>
      <li>Longer lags correlate with Eddington ratio, FeII strength, CIV BALs, and colour</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="references">
      <h2>References</h2>
      <ol>
        <li id="ref1">Steyn, Z., Wolf, C., Onken, C., et al. (2026). "Continuum Reverberation in Bright Quasars Using NASA/ATLAS." <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11789">arXiv:2603.11789</a></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
